    hook_question: 'Term insurance aur life insurance me kya farak hai?',
    hook_question_en: 'What\'s the difference between term insurance and life insurance?',
    viz_body: '<b>Term insurance sirf risk</b> cover deta hai.<br>sasta premium, par maturity par kuch wapas nahi milta agar policy period mein kuch na ho. Traditional (endowment) life insurance mein thoda savings bhi judta hai, par premium zyada hota hai.',
    viz_body_en: '<b>Term insurance only covers</b> risk.<br>cheaper premium, but nothing comes back at maturity if nothing happens during the policy period. Traditional (endowment) life insurance adds some savings too, but the premium is higher.',
