    id: 'digital-arrest-scam',
    tag_category: 'fraud-safety',
    hook_question: 'Agar WhatsApp par koi police ki vardi mein video call karke bole ki aapke naam ka parcel pakda gaya hai, toh kya karenge?',
    hook_question_en: 'If someone in the police uniform video calls you on WhatsApp and says a parcel in your name has been caught, what will you do?',
    viz_body: 'Ise \'Digital Arrest\' scam kehte hain. Asli CBI ya Customs aapse kabhi Skype ya WhatsApp par video call karke paise transfer karne ko nahi kehti.<br>Dariye mat, <b>turant call kaatiye aur 1930 dial karein ya cybercrime.gov.in par report karein</b>.',
    viz_body_en: 'This is called a \'Digital Arrest\' scam. Real CBI or Customs never video calls you on Skype or WhatsApp to transfer money.<br>Do not fear, <b>disconnect the call immediately and dial 1930 or report on cybercrime.gov.in</b>.',
    micro_action: 'Aise call aate hi 1930 dial karein ya cybercrime.gov.in par iski report darj karayein. Ise apne maa-baap ke sath zaroor share karein.',
    micro_action_en: 'As soon as such a call comes, dial 1930 or register a report on cybercrime.gov.in. Definitely share this with your parents.',
