    id: 'google-customer-care-scam',
    tag_category: 'fraud-safety',
    hook_question: 'Swiggy, Zomato ya Bank ka customer care number Google par search karna aapko mehanga pad sakta hai.',
    hook_question_en: 'Searching for Swiggy, Zomato or Bank\'s customer care number on Google can cost you dearly.',
    viz_body: 'Scammers Google ads mein apne farzi number daal dete hain jo bilkul asli customer care jaise lagte hain.<br>Call karne par wo aapse <b>remote access app (jaise AnyDesk) download karwa lete hain</b> aur bank khali kar dete hain.<br><b>Shak hone par turant 1930 dial karein ya cybercrime.gov.in par report karein.</b>',
    viz_body_en: 'Scammers put their fake numbers in Google ads which look exactly like real customer care.<br>Upon calling, they <b>make you download a remote access app (like AnyDesk)</b> and empty the bank.<br><b>Dial 1930 or report on cybercrime.gov.in if suspicious.</b>',
    micro_action: 'Hamesha company ke official app ke andar jaakar \'Help/Support\' se baat karein, kabhi Google search se nahi.',
