    hook_question_en: 'How can those who don\'t have a big touch-screen phone do UPI from a button phone?',
    viz_body: 'NPCI ne \'UPI 123PAY\' banaya hai. Is se sadharan keypad wale phone se bhi payment ho sakti hai.<br>Aap sirf <b>IVR number (jaise 08045163666) par call karke ya missed call se</b> kisi ko bhi paise bhej sakte hain.',
